description:
News of the raid on the Revolutionary Army reaches Luffy! But that`s the least of their worries as they face a storm and a sudden lack of provisions! Meanwhile, Emperor Kaido, furious at the loss of Joker, fumes with anger at the reckless generation of upstarts!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Kaido Returns! An Imminent Threat to the Worst Generation!
Kaidos Rückkehr – Eine Gefahr für die Schlimmste Generation
Kaidou Futatabi: Kyoui Semaru Saiaku no Sedai!
Le retour de Kaido. La pire génération menacée !
Возвращение Кайдо! Опаснейшая угроза для Худшего поколения
عودة كايدو! تهديد وشيك للجيل الأسوأ!
カイドウ再び 脅威迫る最悪の世代!
